---
title: Caribbean Beef & Black Bean Chilli Nachos with Cucumber Salsa & Cheddar
description: We turned the best things about nachos (the crispy chips) into a side for this delectable chilli so you can enjoy maximum crunch!
We've also added cucumber salsa and Cheddar cheese so you can enjoy an explosion of flavour with every bite.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/caribbean-beef-chilli-nachos-e3d4187c.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/caribbean-beef-chilli-nachos-603430348a2d143e537cc406-e545b984.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/caribbean-beef-and-black-bean-chilli-nachos-603430348a2d143e537cc406
servings: 2
cuisine: Caribbean
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
time required: 35 minutes
